metadata.name: Ethereans Official 1
metadata.description: The Ethereans are an army of 11,000 soldiers that came from Planet Crypto, far far away in the ETH Region on the edges of the Milky Way Galaxy. Created by The Chaos Duo in collaboration with PaisanoDAO, this NFT grants you access to exclusive content, airdrops, and utility-related to this and other Chaos Duo IP's.
